## ğŸ” Key Findings
- SQL injection poses high risk due to data exposure and system compromise  
- Buffer overflow threats can lead to total system takeover  
- Phishing remains a major entry point for attackers across all departments  
- Strong access control and consistent training significantly reduce exposure  

